Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Class Either<L,​R>

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.Either<L,​R>
public class Either<L,​R>
extends java.lang.Object
A mini-collection that represents a pair where either the 'left' or the 'right' object exists, i.e. it is not valid to have neither be specified, or both.

      When you are looking at 2 'eithers' of the same type, this helps you separate out when both 'eithers' only have a value on the left side, vs. when both 'eithers' only have a value on the right side. If the non-empty side is not the same for both 'eithers', this will throw.
